long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides a button to open twitter in an incognito window. 

If you have already logged in and have an extra incognito window open, the window will go straight to your twitter account. Otherwise you will have to log in.

Great if you share a computer with someone and don't want to switch accounts.

** This app has no association with twitter. It was made by me **

Feel free to send feedback to my email.
